---
layout: base.njk
title: Our Leadership Team
description: Meet the leadership team at WellCare & Nurture Pediatric Therapy in Colorado Springs.
permalink: /team/
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Our Leadership Team</h1>
    <p>Meet the dedicated professionals leading our multi-disciplinary team</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="team-grid">
      {% for member in collections.team %}
      <div class="team-card">
        <div class="team-card-photo" style="background-image: url('{{ member.data.photo or '/images/team-placeholder.jpg' }}');"></div>
        <div class="team-card-body">
          <h3>{{ member.data.name }}</h3>
          <div class="title">{{ member.data.role }}</div>
          <div class="bio">{{ member.data.bio }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
